{"tid":2462233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3大漢尖嘴截停的士 刀斧鐵鎚斬人 司機乘客同受傷","createTime":"2021-03-26T01:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:27:58.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7215ba85c6eefa9a049a59c6d598336b5be1a310","tid":2462233,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSnD8X9372o8vRBgNmSFDHbbEfURo2ehbwKAzp9KB3ye7?filename=wCGQTRu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCGQTRu.png&h=52e6d48b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尖沙嘴發生傷人血案，早上7時許，一名青年在柯士甸路近漆咸道南截乘的士，車輛開行不久，即有3名男子從一輛黑色凌志私家車衝下，分持斧頭、鐵鎚和刀，狂砸的士擋風玻璃及車窗，然後襲擊司機和乘客，刀手閃電傷人後登回接應私家車逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n救護員趕至現場，的士司機頭部受傷流血，乘客則左手受輕傷，經敷治後一併送院治理，的士內滿佈玻璃碎片及血迹，警員到場展開調查。"},{"pid":"08ca30ae8f381de6ed5a68a49ea90b94be81b040","tid":2462233,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210326/3EKMB3LFVJH5PEKL2JDLSWL5Z4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210326%2F3EKMB3LFVJH5PEKL2JDLSWL5Z4%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=5bf9e216\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210326%2F3EKMB3LFVJH5PEKL2JDLSWL5Z4%2F&h=92c20a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210326/3EKMB3LFVJH5PEKL2JDLSWL5Z4/</a>"},{"pid":"be889f011ff602ed7ac6d17cef046a81947c4f5d","tid":2462233,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:26:33.000Z","msg":"斬斧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105c62e2419d9a5a02514525ccd5a9f486c29689","tid":2462233,"uid":46154,"like":6,"dislik